{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Lesezeichen","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"\n  <ol>\n    <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions\"><strong>Browser extensions</strong></a></li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Getting started</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/What_are_WebExtensions\">What are extensions?</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Your_first_WebExtension\">Your first extension</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Your_second_WebExtension\">Your second extension</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Anatomy_of_a_WebExtension\">Anatomy of an extension</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Examples\">Example extensions</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/What_next_\">What next?</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Concepts</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Using_the_JavaScript_APIs\">Using the JavaScript APIs</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Content_scripts\">Content scripts</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Match_patterns\">Match patterns</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Working_with_files\">Working with files</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Internationalization\">Internationalization</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Content_Security_Policy\">Content Security Policy</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Native_messaging\">Native messaging</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Differences_between_API_implementations\">Differences between API implementations</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Chrome_incompatibilities\">Chrome incompatibilities</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>User interface</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface\">User Interface</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Browser_action\">Toolbar button</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Page_actions\">Address bar button</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Sidebars\">Sidebars</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Context_menu_items\">Context menu items</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Options_pages\">Options page</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Extension_pages\">Extension pages</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Notifications\">Notifications</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Omnibox\">Address bar suggestions</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/devtools_panels\">Developer tools panels</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>How to</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Intercept_HTTP_requests\">Intercept HTTP requests</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Modify_a_web_page\">Modify a web page</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Safely_inserting_external_content_into_a_page\">Insert external content</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Sharing_objects_with_page_scripts\">Share objects with page scripts</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Add_a_button_to_the_toolbar\">Add a button to the toolbar</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Implement_a_settings_page\">Implement a settings page</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Working_with_the_Tabs_API\">Work with the Tabs API</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Work_with_the_Bookmarks_API\">Work with the Bookmarks API</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Work_with_the_Cookies_API\">Work with the Cookies API</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Work_with_contextual_identities\">Work with contextual identities</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Interact_with_the_clipboard\">Interact with the clipboard</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Build_a_cross_browser_extension\">Build a cross-browser extension</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Firefox_differentiators\">Firefox differentiators</a></summary>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details open=\"\">\n        <summary>JavaScript APIs</summary>\n        <ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Browser_support_for_JavaScript_APIs\">Browser support for JavaScript APIs</a></li><li class=\"webextension-api-sidebar\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks\">bookmarks</a><ol></ol></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/commands\">commands</a></li></ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n      <summary>Manifest keys</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json\">Introduction</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      <ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/commands\">commands</a></li></ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n     <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Extension Workshop</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/develop/\">Develop</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/publish/\">Publish</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/manage/\">Manage</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/enterprise/\">Enterprise</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/Contact_us\"><strong>Contact us</strong></a></li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Channels</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"https://blog.mozilla.org/addons\">Add-ons blog</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://discourse.mozilla.org/c/add-ons\">Add-ons forum</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://chat.mozilla.org/#/room/%23addons:mozilla.org\">Add-ons chat</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n  </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Die <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions\">WebExtensions</a> <a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>bookmarks</code></a> API erlaubt es einer Erweiterung mit dem Lesezeichensystem des Browsers interagieren und dieses zu manipulieren. Sie können die API verwenden, um für Seiten Lesezeichen zu setzen, vorhandene Lesezeichen abzurufen und Lesezeichen zu bearbeiten, zu entfernen und zu organisieren.</p>\n\n<p>Um diese API zu verwenden, muss die Erweiterung die <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/permissions\">Berechtigung</a> \"Lesezeichen\" in der <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json\">manifest.json</a></code> Datei besitzen.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"types","title":"Types","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.bookmarktreenodeunmodifiable\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/BookmarkTreeNodeUnmodifiable\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.BookmarkTreeNodeUnmodifiable (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Ein <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>String</code></a> enum, das angibt, warum ein Lesezeichen oder ein Ordner unmodifizierbar ist.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.bookmarktreenode\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/BookmarkTreeNode\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.BookmarkTreeNode (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Stellt ein Lesezeichen oder einen Ordner im Lesezeichenbaum dar.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.createdetails\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/CreateDetails\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.CreateDetails (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Enthält Informationen, die bei der Erstellung eines neuen Lesezeichens an die <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/create\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.create() (en-US)</a> Funktion übergeben werden.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"functions","title":"Functions","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.create\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/create\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.create() (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Erstellt ein Lesezeichen oder Ordner.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.get\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/get\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.get() (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Ruft eine oder mehrere <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/BookmarkTreeNode\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">BookmarkTreeNode (en-US)</a> ab und übergibt eine Lesezeichen-ID oder ein Array von Lesezeichen ID.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.getchildren\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/getChildren\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.getChildren() (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Ruft die Kinder des angegebenen <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/BookmarkTreeNode\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">BookmarkTreeNode (en-US)</a> ab.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.getrecent\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/getRecent\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.getRecent() (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Ruft eine angeforderte Anzahl von zuletzt hinzugefügten Lesezeichen ab.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.getsubtree\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/getSubTree\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.getSubTree() (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Ruft einen Teil des Lesezeichenbaums ab und beginnt am angegebenen Knoten.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.gettree\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/getTree\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.getTree() (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Ruft den gesamten Lesezeichenbaum in ein Array von <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/BookmarkTreeNode\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">BookmarkTreeNode (en-US)</a> Objekte auf.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.move\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/move\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.move() (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Moves the specified <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/BookmarkTreeNode\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">BookmarkTreeNode (en-US)</a> to a new location in the bookmark tree.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.remove\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/remove\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.remove() (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Removes a bookmark or an empty bookmark folder, given the node's ID.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.removetree\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/removeTree\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.removeTree() (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Recursively removes a bookmark folder; that is, given the ID of a folder node, removes that node and all its descendants.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.search\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/search\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.search() (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Searches for <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/BookmarkTreeNode\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">BookmarkTreeNode (en-US)</a>s matching a specified set of criteria.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.update\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/update\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.update() (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Updates the title and/or URL of a bookmark, or the name of a bookmark folder, given the bookmark's ID.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"events","title":"Events","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.oncreated\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/onCreated\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.onCreated (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Fired when a bookmark or folder is created.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.onremoved\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/onRemoved\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.onRemoved (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Fired when a bookmark or folder is removed. When a folder is removed recursively, a single notification is fired for the folder, and none for its contents.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.onchanged\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/onChanged\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.onChanged (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Fired when a bookmark or folder changes. Currently, only <code>title</code> and <code>url</code> changes trigger this.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.onmoved\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/onMoved\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.onMoved (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Fired when a bookmark or folder is moved to a different parent folder or to a new offset within its folder.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.onchildrenreordered\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/onChildrenReordered\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.onChildrenReordered (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Fired when the user has sorted the children of a folder in the browser's UI. This is not called as a result of a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/move\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">move() (en-US)</a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.onimportbegan\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/onImportBegan\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.onImportBegan (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Fired when a bookmark import session is begun. Expensive observers should ignore <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/onCreated\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.onCreated (en-US)</a> updates until <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/onImportEnded\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.onImportEnded (en-US)</a> is fired. Observers should still handle other notifications immediately.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bookmarks.onimportended\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/onImportEnded\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">bookmarks.onImportEnded (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Fired when a bookmark import session has finished.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"webextensions.api.bookmarks","dataURL":"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"edge_incompatibilities","title":"Edge incompatibilities","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Promises are not supported in Edge. Use callbacks instead.</p>\n\n<p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example_extensions","title":"Example extensions","isH3":false,"content":"<ul><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/bookmark-it\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bookmark-it</a></li></ul><p></p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\"><strong>Acknowledgements</strong>\n\n<p>This API is based on Chromium's <a href=\"https://developer.chrome.com/extensions/bookmarks\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\"><code>chrome.bookmarks</code></a> API. This documentation is derived from <a href=\"https://chromium.googlesource.com/chromium/src/+/master/chrome/common/extensions/api/bookmarks.json\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\"><code>bookmarks.json</code></a> in the Chromium code.</p>\n\n<p>Microsoft Edge compatibility data is supplied by Microsoft Corporation and is included here under the Creative Commons Attribution 3.0 United States License.</p>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Types","id":"types"},{"text":"Functions","id":"functions"},{"text":"Events","id":"events"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Example extensions","id":"example_extensions"}],"summary":"Die WebExtensions bookmarks API erlaubt es einer Erweiterung mit dem Lesezeichensystem des Browsers interagieren und dieses zu manipulieren. Sie können die API verwenden, um für Seiten Lesezeichen zu setzen, vorhandene Lesezeichen abzurufen und Lesezeichen zu bearbeiten, zu entfernen und zu organisieren.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"bookmarks","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"bookmarks","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"bookmarks","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"bookmarks","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"bookmarks","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/mozilla/add-ons/webextensions/api/bookmarks","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/mozilla/add-ons/webextensions/api/bookmarks/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Mozilla","title":"Mozilla"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons","title":"Add-ons"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions","title":"WebExtensions"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API","title":"JavaScript APIs"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks","title":"Lesezeichen"}],"pageTitle":"Lesezeichen - Mozilla | MDN","noIndexing":false}}